Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So between your organic brown rice and jogging, they're all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All the, all my brown bagger colleagues are dead.
