Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:22:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So the credibility of authority is also, today authority is viewed with great suspicion.
