Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The seductions that you walk through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.32,0:22:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And one is the seduction of the astral circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the astral circus also is very high in glamour.
