Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.99,0:25:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.85,0:25:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, out of humility, then, the teacher says, avoid that which is beyond your comprehension
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.53,0:25:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because they come from other dimensions and their idea of reality and their motivations
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.38,0:25:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and their style of functioning is totally out of your domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.85,0:26:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And the presumptions that you make are fallacious, though you've projected that onto the entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.77,0:26:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is no particular interest in your survival or your spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.75,0:26:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.75,0:26:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.75,0:26:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the right to go away from something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.75,0:26:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own choice, whether it be Your spiritual evolution or your enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.75,0:26:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A successful student would quickly quit the teacher from the other side.
