Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.75,0:26:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.81,0:26:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,child, the trusting child within, but what we call paradigm blindness. What is true in one paradigm
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.79,0:26:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is not true in another paradigm. Paradigm includes then the overall level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.39,0:27:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's true in one paradigm is not true in another paradigm. So the difficulty of the doubter,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.73,0:27:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the traditional skeptic, is usually coming from lower mind, which deals only in the linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.89,0:27:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,linear provability. And spiritual dimensions are non-linear, not provable. That which is provable
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.00,0:27:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is of a different dimension. So you cannot disprove the non-linear using arguments from
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.79,0:27:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the linear. And that's why the skeptic only calibrates the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.44,0:27:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about 170. And all the debunkers, there's only one or two debunkers that are actually
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.24,0:27:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,integrityists. There's only a few of them. The rest of them just get an ego kick out of trying
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.90,0:27:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to imitate what's real. And then because they've imitated it, they assume they have disproven it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.90,0:28:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Because you can imitate a thing doesn't mean you've disproven it. It just means you've
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.43,0:28:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,learned how to imitate a thing. And the great Randy, for instance, is a stage
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.47,0:28:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,mediator.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.71,0:28:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,magician, stage magician. Therefore, coming from the linear, you can neither prove nor disprove
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.44,0:28:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the non-linear. In all spiritual reality, all understanding of divinity and spiritual truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.30,0:28:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, is of a different dimension than the linear. The linear is provable and demonstrable.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.36,0:28:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The non-linear is more profound and diffuse. And of course, create the alters. You can show
