Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.06,0:28:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,quite a delay. When you're in a hundred-yard dash, nine-tenths of a second will lose you the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.67,0:28:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a profound influence on our behavior and our understanding, our motivation.
